#### A. 打扑克
http://csp.ac/contest/37/problem/265

猜结论题，当$n=2$时先手必胜，否则如果$n$是奇数且皮蛋先手则皮蛋胜，否则黑妞胜。

```cpp
#include<cstdio>

int t;

int main() {
	scanf("%d", &t);
	while (t--) {
		int n, op, bit = 0;
		char c = getchar();
		while (c != ' ') {
			if ('0' <= c && c <= '9') n = c - '0', bit++;
			c = getchar();
		}
		scanf("%d", &op);
		if (n == 2 && bit == 1) printf("%d\n", op);
